These chroot construction scripts will install a
chroot in /usr3/chroots suitable for building kernels.

All of these scripts will ask for a sudo password.

Sample invocations:

$ make_chroot maverick amd64 http://archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu
$ make_chroot maverick armel http://ports.ubuntu.com/ubuntu-ports
$ make_release maverick http://archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu http://ports.ubuntu.com/ubuntu-ports
$ make_all

$ remove_chroot maverick amd64
$ remove_release maverick
$ remove_all
